  The US President must save the Earth from alien overlord Zinyak using an
  arsenal of superpowers and strange weapons in the wildest open world game
  ever.                                                                     
                                                                            
  The epic conclusion to the game that changed all the rules! The Saints have
  gone from the crackhouse to the White House - but the Earth has been invaded
  and it's up to you to free the world from Overlord Zinyak and his alien
  empire. With homies new and old by your side, and an arsenal of superpowers
